{"tid":1930358,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"星展料香港上半年失業率近5%　全年樓價跌15%","createTime":"2020-03-17T13:13:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-21T01:24:45.000Z","uid":101341,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"9d745afa9fdf6a399f7d6502d991face73ce6956","tid":1930358,"uid":101341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T13:13:55.000Z","msg":"星展香港經濟研究部經濟師謝家曦預計，香港上半年失業率升至近5%，根據過去經驗，失業率達5%以上，樓價會跌10%。他指，失業率對樓價有滯後影響，預計今年樓價跌15%。<br />\n<br />\n匯市方面，星展認為，港息高於美息，吸引資金流入，但資金未必流向股市，因為環球避險情緒高漲，相信市民傾向持有現金。<br />\n<br />\n另外，星展香港經濟研究部首席中國經濟師梁兆基認為，貨幣政策未能對症下藥，解決新型肺炎疫情帶來的現金流危機，因為銀行見到市場風險高的時候，放貸利率亦會上升。<br />\n<br />\n梁兆基認為，股市可能在疫情後呈V型反彈，但實體經濟絕對不會，如果中央希望經濟復蘇具持續性，政策應該盡量確保企業不會倒閉，因為中小企佔中國50%稅收、60%國內生產總值，以及80%就業。他認為，內地至少要減稅2-3年，才可以說服企業仍有前景。"},{"pid":"cf00174030bc8101a781f72281da87f40ebcf0a7","tid":1930358,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T13:15:20.000Z","msg":"專家：全年樓價跌15%<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d12cd57e0842ac84151f38955314d5c8ef13269b","tid":1930358,"uid":259532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T13:15:52.000Z","msg":"驚閪"},{"pid":"70cd68e4f323ec0c5adf0e5922f1e2ce82aaf9a9","tid":1930358,"uid":109923,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T13:16:45.000Z","msg":"10%失業先算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qn39Y8p.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fqn39Y8p.gif&h=f3317ef8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7Ej5xtp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7Ej5xtp.jpg&h=44dedd06&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9b254c4af3bc7589f751d63753e8ec1b76730ace","tid":1930358,"uid":101341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"70cd68e4f323ec0c5adf0e